Comment: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:46.96,Note,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Dirac Sea: A theoretical model for a vacuum as a sea of infinite particles. One of the Angels in Evangelion generates such a sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.69,0:00:05.23,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,When watching TV,  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:06.74,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,make sure the room is well lit, 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.91,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,and watch from a distance. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:09.95,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Got it? 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:20.80,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Klaus Seishirou. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:24.92,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a retired butler who now lives as a farmer in Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:29.11,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I haven't retired yet! 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.56,0:00:32.19,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I will be a Sanzenin butler to the very end! 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.19,0:00:34.73,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing left for you to do. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:40.48,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,We even found a replacement for Himegami,\Nso you don't have anything to worry about, do you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:42.83,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,How dare an animal try to understand my feelings?! 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:45.74,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it bother you more that an animal is talking? 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.74,0:00:50.67,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,That impoverished butler looks like he can handle the selfish lady. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.99,0:00:53.35,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave it to a rookie like him. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.35,0:00:54.17,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to Japan! 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:00:55.98,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:59.30,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to spend what's left of your time here in Brazil with me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:00.99,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's... 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:03.26,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's... 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.64,0:01:06.49,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Tama! Was that you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:09.43,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,We're starting off with a dream this week? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:11.75,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Now farewell, everyone. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:15.54,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,No, a tiger can't possibly talk. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.54,0:01:17.16,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I must be tired. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:20.69,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.07,0:01:26.36,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Looking to be a coffee plantation owner in Brazil? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:28.15,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,When was this put here? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:35.47,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,One who masters being a butler becomes the master of the world. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:41.15,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Butler War that shakes the planet has started! 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.98,0:01:44.79,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,The kanji for my name is made of "Kura", as in warehouse, and "Usu", as in mortar. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:46.85,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I am pure-bred Japanese! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:30.71,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect temperature. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:36.82,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Ironing the newspaper. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:39.26,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,This is a butler's first chore in the morning. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:47.81,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, postponing the release of\NDragon ***** is causing the stock to drop. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:55.34,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I had a strange dream of being an owner of\Na coffee bean plantation in Brazil and doing nothing. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:57.65,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:01.22,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to retire, go ahead. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:02.75,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,What?! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:04.42,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:06.87,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I plan on burying my bones with the Sanzenin family! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:09.24,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,That was only a dream I had! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:13.77,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,According to Freud, a dream is a vision of your hidden desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:18.62,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,So deep down, you feel tired and want to retire. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:20.57,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not true! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:23.13,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, what would happen to\Nthe Sanzenin family if I disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:24.82,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:28.33,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate and Maria take care of everyday things. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:31.38,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,If it's about asset management, you don't have to worry. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:35.30,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You can't handle IT-related stocks, can you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:39.22,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we'll be fine. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:48.48,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I mustn't run away. I mustn't run away. I mustn't run away. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:51.24,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I mustn't run away. I mustn't run away. I mustn't run away. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.97,Default-alt,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Klaus-san? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:54.54,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,An A* Field. It's a barrier made by the soul. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:55.55,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-san! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:59.30,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:02.95,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened to Klaus-san; he's so depressed. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:05.98,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Maybe he suffered a great shock? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:11.42,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. But I did say that he can retire. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:14.54,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to take his dream seriously. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:17.16,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, a butler who served for years would... 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:24.60,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,...receive a room in the mansion and live like a family member. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.83,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,He must have been shocked to hear you say retire. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:30.84,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't possibly quit because of that! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:36.09,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady. So you like Klaus-san deep down in your heart. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:39.44,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's only a character who's easy to fool around with. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:42.49,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't tell him to quit. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:46.96,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, he might be getting consumed by the Dirac Sea. {WHAT? Something like Dylafk no Ul. Anyone with clue?}{Dei- check}{Al - okay, this is going to sound dumb as hell, but I heard dirac no umi -> the Dirac sea. It's a term for this http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dirac_sea . As dumb as this sounds, I think it may be right since it's referenced in Eva and we just had an Eva reference}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:47.44,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I agree. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:50.33,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Then get a forced salvage operation going or something! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:52.53,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:54.28,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What was that giggle about? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:56.42,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:02.37,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Chief butler. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:06.36,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Maria. I've resigned from my job. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:08.97,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I will now spend the rest of my life in Brazil. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:13.53,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's obvious she wasn't serious when she said you can retire. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:14.83,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,But! But! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:18.40,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,If you have your mind made up, then there's nothing I can do. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:18.89,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.89,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let Milady know. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:25.47,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What Milady said has merit! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:29.32,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,There must be a loose end in my heart for me to have a dream of retirement. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:33.40,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I will return to the days when I aimed to becoming a footman! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:34.38,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Footman? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:38.84,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Footmen are people who work under butlers. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:41.71,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,So you know, there are no footmen in the Sanzenin. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:45.85,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,As a footman, I challenge Ayasaki Hayate to see who can serve Milady better! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:48.69,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What a roundabout way of doing this. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:50.99,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,Way to ruin it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:53.46,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,And I was almost able to go to Brazil. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:59.39,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,A fight to see who can serve Milady better? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:02.68,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall asking for any of this. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:05.16,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,It's what Klaus-san started. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:08.98,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Boy! You indeed learned a lot in a short period of time! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:11.74,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,But, you have a fatal flaw! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:14.15,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What? Where? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:16.21,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Like how you look so cute when you cross-dress. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:17.18,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:21.13,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Boy. Butlers are supposed to be their master's shadow. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:23.58,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, you have an attitude like that of a main character. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:26.23,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,In fact he is, so there's nothing he can do about that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:29.34,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's more of a reserved type of main character. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:31.48,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a compliment? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:37.98,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, for the next 24 hours,\Nwe will use all of our skills as butlers to serve Lady Nagi. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:42.09,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,If she finds me inferior to you, 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:43.94,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I will leave this mansion! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:52.18,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I will do my best as to not be rude to the chief butler. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:08:00.73,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And so the who-can-serve-Milady-better battle started. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:06.74,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Boy. Do you know what the most necessary attribute of a butler is? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:12.39,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe like how they're hated in episode one, but they are loved by the final episode, 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:16.69,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,or swapping bodies with the master from a strange cause and solving mysteries? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:17.97,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,No! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:20.09,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,It's the inspiration to read ahead! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:24.38,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,You need the strength to read ahead\Nand understand what the master wants. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:29.29,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,A noble's morning starts with a morning tea. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:32.08,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's already taken care of. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:32.80,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,What? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.63,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It's ready, Milady. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:37.90,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Hayate. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:39.99,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:45.57,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,In England, it's an important job where they even have a person in charge of making tea! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.57,0:08:49.26,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't know the proper way of making it,\Nyou can't call yourself a butler! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:52.83,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It is a teabag the English royal palace uses. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.83,0:08:54.23,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,What? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:56.46,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds nice. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:58.84,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to use lemon or milk? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:04.84,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! Lemon tea does not exist in England! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:09.72,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that starts the morning is milk tea prepared by the butler with his fine-tuned pouring skill! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:10.63,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go with lemon. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:11.88,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:16.34,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,The lemon tea you make is great, Hayate. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.94,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.49,Default-alt,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This can't be... 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:21.40,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, go easy on him a little.	 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:26.85,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,No... No... You got it wrong... 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:32.39,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,So you will go to school today, Milady? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:36.25,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Since I feel bad fooling around with Klaus too much. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:38.24,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Then why do you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:41.29,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus and I go back many years. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:45.14,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Because we know each other well,\Nit's fun to fool around with each other. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:55.86,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we get two extra drumsticks. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.51,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,And it comes with nuggets, too. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:02.35,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are they low on chicken stock? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:11.79,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he didn't come chasing us this far. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:13.09,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:13.89,Default-alt,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,You there! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:16.09,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:17.83,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:27.04,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's a perfectly polished piece of silverware. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:29.71,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,And that's a sign of a professional butler! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:36.40,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Boy! I quit being human! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:37.18,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus-san! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:40.35,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're a Sanzenin butler! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:43.81,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Uriiiiiiiiiiii! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:49.73,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,The origin of the word "butler" comes from "bouteiller", the position of those who take care of wine cellars. {spelling?} 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:53.83,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Wine... A vintage wine... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:56.30,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Violet Over Drive! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:10:58.97,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Bordeaux... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.71,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Burgundy! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.84,Default-alt,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,These are no wines for a drunk to drink! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.00,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Zugyuuuuun! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:04.73,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:07.02,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them have left. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:08.12,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:14.77,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,The best thing to do on a sunny day like this is to skip classes. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:18.47,Default,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking that everyone else is studying makes me relax even more. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.04,0:11:24.22,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,And things would be perfect if we had a butler who would make tea for us. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:28.37,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Sunlight **** Over Drive! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:33.37,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,A dummy? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:36.67,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Butler ninja skill: Dummy no Jitsu.{Al - added in this, no tl probably needed even}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.77,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,She was an unexpected interference. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.73,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,And now- 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:43.57,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,M-My back... 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:48.96,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's Nagi-chan's place's chief butler! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:54.93,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Tomarigi sagashitemasu. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:54.93,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Tomarigi sagashitemasu = I'm searching for a branch to land on. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:11:59.90,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,Suppai Omoide daze. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:11:59.90,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Suppai Omoide daze = What a sour memory. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.74,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:07.03,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,It's premier cake and tea! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:08.12,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:12.01,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted the people who saved my life to enjoy it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:13.93,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.93,0:12:15.45,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,Itadakimasu. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:18.04,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank you", huh... 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:20.37,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is his master's shadow. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:24.72,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,But inside, they are waiting for that one word of gratitude. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:27.63,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,It's better than what we find at the store by the train station. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:29.97,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,This tea is fabulous, too. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:30.80,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,It's exquisite. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:31.86,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I found you! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:33.01,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Katsura-chan! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:33.81,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiji! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.10,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,There's a reason behind this. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.88,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, I don't care! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:38.67,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Give me some, too! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:43.05,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:44.37,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb with me! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:46.28,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,You have some vintage wine, don't you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:48.41,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiji looks dangerous. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:48.41,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.86,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:51.67,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you being violent against the elderly? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:53.02,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,"Elderly"?! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:55.44,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,He came falling from the sky a while ago. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:58.28,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,He's an old man to whom no one knows what may happen at any moment. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:12:59.78,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,RIP. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:01.44,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, but... 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:05.03,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,K-Klaus-san? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:09.89,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,How far did he go? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:13.21,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure Klaus has recovered from it by now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:15.79,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus-san! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:28.82,Default,Him,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if it isn't Klaus-san, a legendary figure in the butler world. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:32.50,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm right, you must be the Oukouchi family's butler. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:34.81,Default,Him,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Saeki Himuro. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:37.03,Default,Him,0000,0000,0000,,And this is Sir Taiga. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:40.13,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pretend I didn't hear that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.01,Default,Him,0000,0000,0000,,What? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:45.70,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Traditionally, it is the butler's pride\Nto be called under their master's name. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:49.66,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,The Oukouchi's butler doesn't even know that? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:52.19,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Himuro? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:54.19,Default,Him,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, the flowers. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:55.61,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:14:01.14,Default,Him,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Heisei era, and you speak like Edward. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:04.46,Default,Him,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad to see the famous butler aging. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:09.85,Default,Him,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad for you to cling to your former status. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:16.74,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're amazing, Himuro! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:22.12,Default,Him,0000,0000,0000,,With your reflexes, you can't protect your master in an emergency. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:26.39,Default,Him,0000,0000,0000,,How about you retire and think of a new life for yourself? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:30.38,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,You're still young, Oukouchi butler. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:31.68,Default,Him,0000,0000,0000,,What? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:34.51,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I am my master's shadow. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:37.37,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,A shadow does not have a private life to begin with. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:43.29,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,When you realize you can't be of aid to\Nyour master anymore, you just disappear. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:50.64,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think... 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:53.53,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,...he decided to retire because of that, do you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:54.41,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.53,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Is he serious? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:06.46,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there any way to have Klaus-san stay? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:08.58,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,There is a hidden trick. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:09.91,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Really? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:15.27,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but you'll have go through a little change. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:19.26,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you mean lend a little hand. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:23.90,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've got a bad feeling... 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:32.89,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is all a memory now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:39.03,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,My life was spent with these Sanzenin\Nand my bones were supposed to be buried here. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:43.46,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,But what the Oukouchi's young butler says has merit. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:46.69,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time I step down. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.50,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus-san. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:04.60,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're from sometime ago... 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:11.92,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,You're the pillar of my heart I saw in the garden sometime ago! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:14.57,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a genius. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:19.29,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate-kun's feminine sex appeal really works. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:22.36,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Klaus-san will feel better after this. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:25.37,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is your name? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:26.61,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasaki- 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:28.95,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasaki? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:31.77,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hermione. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:33.96,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hermione! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:38.31,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,What a fantastic name! Sounds like you can use magic. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:44.56,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... In fact, I'm a goddess that resides in Lake Sanzenin. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:48.65,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I knew you weren't an ordinary woman. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:56.39,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus-san. I've always been watching you from the bottom of the lake. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:57.97,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:17:00.37,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You must not quit the chief butler position. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:03.22,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You're not that old yet. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:06.64,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:10.86,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I've become so old my hair is all white. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:12.77,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:14.81,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice romantic grey. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:17.82,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think so, too? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:20.43,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,People often say that to me\Nat Ikebukuro's adult social gatherings.{Al - what's Ikebukuro?} 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:23.14,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Then you won't think about retiring, will you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:26.39,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,But lately, my shoulders have been getting stiff, and I can't keep them up. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:29.69,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sure it can be massaged off. {Dei- tlcheck} 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:30.57,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,See? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:37.70,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Look how hard it is. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:41.67,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do my back and waist, too? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:42.84,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:47.10,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, right there. That's where I like it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:51.05,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Be convinced already, you egghead geezer. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:55.58,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Klaus talking to? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:58.12,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,More to this side. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.01,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't touch there. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:02.13,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,I-Itadakimasu! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:08.50,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Hermione-san... I-I've... 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:08.18,Default-alt,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,Honey! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:16.29,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I've aged enough to hallucinate, huh? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:18.24,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,It had the reverse effect... 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.51,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,This stupid tiger. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:26.12,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:33.60,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:37.16,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Tama... Don't tell me you were after this female tiger... 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:39.98,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,I fell in love with her. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:43.32,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,But as a tiger, I can't go to Brazil alone. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:45.47,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you tried to use Klaus-san? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:48.66,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,You will want to go to a plantation in Brazil. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:51.50,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go... You want to go... 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:54.08,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I said! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:55.60,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you one thing. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:19:00.94,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger's don't exist in Brazil! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:12.76,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah. I'll tell him the dream of Brazil he had isn't because of his underlying mental state, but Tama's planning. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:19.50,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't. Nobody knows that Tama can talk. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:03.39,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus! What's the language of flowers for this? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:06.32,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,It's loyalty to my Milady. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:07.48,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Really? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:09.95,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I just decided. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:15.73,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give this to you! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.04,0:20:20.98,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Nagi... 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:28.05,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus-san. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:30.59,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus-san. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:33.68,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, boy. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:36.88,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't anything that you can't do that I can. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.15,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hayate! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:40.31,Default,Kal,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Nagi. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:44.96,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Today's Butler Economics and Industry Newspaper is drenched in morning dew! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:46.79,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I can't read the stock market section well! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:56.02,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Chief butler. I've yet to learn how to iron the newspaper. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:57.05,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Boy! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:21:01.12,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't even iron a newspaper, then Klaus wins the match. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:02.54,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Milady! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:05.71,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Get moving, Klaus! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:12.32,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,You leave me no choice. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:20.69,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect temperature. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:26.62,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Klaus-san has recovered. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:27.20,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:29.53,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, Milady. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:31.87,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,He is part of the Sanzenin family. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:34.51,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be the one who kicked him out. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:39.01,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,How about I make some lemon tea? 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:39.98,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:53.66,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next week, instead of fighting,\Nwe'll try to coexist with small animals. 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:31.46,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru and, 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:31.96,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Saki's, 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.96,0:23:33.06,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Network! 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.59,0:23:35.91,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,A bright smile and ample stock. 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.91,0:23:38.77,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the manager of Rental Video Tachibana, Tachibana Wataru. 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:40.48,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,And I take care of him. 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:41.63,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,His maid, Kijima Saki. 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.63,0:23:46.19,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we have the store's image song,\Nhow about we make some merchandising goods next? 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.19,0:23:48.77,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,But what would appeal to the public? 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.77,0:23:53.79,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,How about giving out the happy-embarrassing photo of Video Tachibana's cult maid, Saki, 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.79,0:23:56.31,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,since we've seen people coming to see you recently? 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.31,0:23:58.63,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Stop joking, Sir! 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.63,0:23:59.92,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,TA-CHI-BANA. 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.30,0:24:04.35,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate. What type of girls do you like? 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.35,0:24:05.96,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see... 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.96,0:24:08.36,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I guess normal girls. 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.36,0:24:08.95,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Normal? 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.95,0:24:11.88,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think someone like you would understand. 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.88,0:24:16.17,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of me! Are you saying that I can't be your ideal kind of girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.17,0:24:17.81,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Hayate no Gotoku. 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:20.61,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I Want to Return to Being a Normal Girl. But Do Buy my Character Song. 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.61,0:24:23.51,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So Hayate-kun likes normal girls. 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.51,0:24:28.65,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know, in Okinawa, the statues of lions you see at lion mansions are of Shisa. {Shisa is a lion god in Okinawa. There is an enterprise that sells mansion, and they are commonly called the Lions Mansion because they have a statue of lion by the gate. Here, they didn't specify as the Lions Mansion, so I left it lower case with "a".} 
